architecture:

Linux:
    PulseAudio/PipeWire monitor
        ↓
    16kHz mono PCM
        ↓
    Vosk


Windows:
    WASAPI loopback via soundcard
        ↓
    16kHz mono PCM
        ↓
    Vosk


macOS:
    avfoundation
        ↓
    16kHz mono PCM
        ↓
    Vosk